Class PeerSocketChannel

java.lang.Object
  org.jboss.netty.channel.AbstractChannel
      org.lantern.PeerSocketChannel
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<org.jboss.netty.channel.Channel>, org.jboss.netty.channel.Channel, org.jboss.netty.channel.socket.SocketChannel
public class PeerSocketChannel
extends org.jboss.netty.channel.AbstractChannel
implements org.jboss.netty.channel.socket.SocketChannel

A Channel wrapping an already connected peer proxy socket. this is largely cargo-culted from org.jboss.netty.channel.socket.oio.OioSocketChannel and org.jboss.netty.channel.socket.oio.OioClientSocketChannel which are irritatingly non-public, much like this class.
